<p>The BrainBashers website also uses other third-party advertising networks certified by Google (a list of which can be seen here <a href="https://www.google.com/adsense/support/bin/answer.py?answer=94149">https://www.google.com/adsense/support/bin/answer.py?answer=94149</a>). You may visit any of those websites to opt out of the cookies used in personalised advertising, if the vendor or ad network offers this capability. Alternatively, you can opt out of some third-party vendors' use of cookies for personalised advertising by visiting <a href="http://www.aboutads.info/choices/">aboutads.info</a>.</p>
<P>Our advertising partners may also use web beacons to collect information as a result of ad serving on our website.</p>
